<html>
  <head>
    <meta charset='utf-8' />
    <meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0' />
    <title>Auction Result</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        line-height: 1.6;
        color: #333;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
      }
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px 0;
        background-color: #4a47d5;
        color: white;
      }
      .content {
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
      }
      .button {
        display: inline-block;
        padding: 10px 20px;
        background-color: #4a47d5;
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin: 10px 5px;
      }
      .footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #777;
      }
      .auction-box {
        border: 1px solid #ddd;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        background-color: #fff;
      }
      .bid-info {
        margin: 10px 0;
      }
      .your-bid {
        color: #dc3545;
      }
      .winning-bid {
        color: #28a745;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      .recommendation {
        background-color: #e9f7fd;
        border-left: 4px solid #4a47d5;
        padding: 10px 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class='container'>
      <div class='header'>
        <h1>Auction Result</h1>
      </div>
      <div class='content'>
        <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
        <p>Thank you for participating in the following auction:</p>

        <div class='auction-box'>
          <h2>{{auctionTitle}}</h2>
          <p class='bid-info your-bid'>Your highest bid: ${{yourBid}}</p>
          <p class='bid-info winning-bid'>Winning bid: ${{winningBid}}</p>
        </div>

        <p>Unfortunately, your bid was not the highest in this auction. We
          encourage you to explore our other exciting auctions that might
          interest you.</p>

        <div class='recommendation'>
          <p><strong>Don't give up!</strong>
            We have many more auctions available that might match your
            interests.</p>
        </div>

        <div style='text-align: center;'>
          <a href='{{allAuctionsUrl}}' class='button'>Browse More Auctions</a>
          <a href='{{auctionUrl}}' class='button'>View Auction Details</a>
        </div>

        <p>We appreciate your participation and hope to see you in future
          auctions!</p>
        <p>Best regards,<br />The QuickBidz Team</p>
      </div>
      <div class='footer'>
        <p>If you have any questions, please contact us at support@quickbidz.com</p>
        <p>&copy; 2023 QuickBidz. All rights reserved.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>